@startuml
title Governance Approval Flow
actor Requester
participant Orchestrator
participant Governance
participant Approver
participant Executor

Requester -> Orchestrator : risky action request
Orchestrator -> Governance : policy evaluation
Governance -> Approver : approval needed
Approver -> Governance : approve / reject
Governance -> Orchestrator : decision
Orchestrator -> Executor : proceed or deny
@enduml
